  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help Sauser Introduce South African Kids to Bikes</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Cycling can change a life. It did for Christoph Sauser, and through his foundation, songo.info, it could do the same for children of South Africa&apos;s townships.  For songo.info, the bike is a key tool that promotes total well-being for kids that have little else. Our key requirements are to upgrade our BMX and MTB program, obtain a vehicle to transport kids to races and events, and to build a clubhouse for after-school and weekend activities, and indoor training, as well after-school support.</narrative>
  </description>
